CRITICAL RULES
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

HEADING IDs MUST NEVER APPEAR IN para_identifiers:
Before writing the JSON, check every ID in every para_identifiers list.
Ask: "Does this paragraph's full text contain legal obligations or definitions?"
If the answer is NO — it is a heading — remove it from the list.

NO FALSE POSITIVES:
Do not report a topic as additional absent if any substantive paragraph covers it,
even if that paragraph is not under a related heading.

PARA IDs MAY APPEAR UNDER MULTIPLE CLAUSES:
One paragraph may address multiple clause topics. Include it wherever it applies.

NO HALLUCINATION:
Never include a paragraph ID not present in the CONTRACT PARAGRAPHS above.

